Class ConcurrentArrayList<K>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.h2.mvstore.ConcurrentArrayList<K>
  • Type Parameters:
    K - the key type

    public class ConcurrentArrayList<K>
extends java.lang.Object
    A very simple array list that supports concurrent access. Internally, it uses immutable objects.
